{"fileHash":"sha256:b4611050e7f863fbb1e4058f555d0a1348e4b207dd9a8b6a8ffc6ac3af7c2db9","sections":{"h2-before-you-start":{"contentHash":"sha256:0f0c62a38bb8c4ac8e04a7990e8756d7e746533b356d2156c92a3f80c8cdc65a","proseHash":"sha256:0f0c62a38bb8c4ac8e04a7990e8756d7e746533b356d2156c92a3f80c8cdc65a","translation":"## 开始之前 \\{#before-you-start\\}\n"},"h3-manage-users":{"contentHash":"sha256:272d1aba66975b1ba841444262b74630e121aa89c2951e2ca8769a11ae0e0162","proseHash":"sha256:272d1aba66975b1ba841444262b74630e121aa89c2951e2ca8769a11ae0e0162","translation":"### 管理用户 \\{#manage-users\\}\n\n您可以选择使用或不使用后端身份验证。\n\n但是，Adapty SDK 对匿名用户和已识别用户的处理方式不同。请阅读[身份识别快速入门指南](react-native-quickstart-identify)，了解其中的差异，确保正确处理用户数据。\n"}}}